   Preventive Services

   Access to scientific evidence, recommendations on clinical preventive
   services, and information on how to implement recommended preventive
   services in clinical practice.

   New Releases in Preventive Services

   Subscribe: AHRQ's Prevention Program LISTSERVÂ®

   U.S. Preventive Services Task Force (USPSTF) Put Prevention Into
   Practice (PPIP)

   An independent panel of experts in primary care and prevention that
   systematically reviews the evidence of effectiveness and develops
   recommendations for clinical preventive services.

